            <div type="translation" source="#borkowski1981" xml:lang="fr">
                <p> Vive Kalotychos et Doros le Jeune! Vive les <hi rend="italic">gennaiotatoi</hi> Verts! 
                     De la tête aux pieds est tombé la faction des Bleus et . . .</p>
                
            </div>  
            
             
           <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
               <p><note>a</note>: The fortune triumphs of Kalotychos and the young Doros.   
                   <note>b</note>: The fortune triumphs of most noble Greens. 
                   <note>c</note>: The Blue has fallen from top to bottom, and [ . . . ] with them</p>
                
         </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                
            <p>Kalotychos and Doros are both acclaimed in other texts on the seats in the auditorium.</p> 
                
            </div>
            
